OL,3,CNorth Sea has 'much more to do' to
OL,4,Cmeet emissions targets for 2040 onwards
OL,6,FOil and gas producers in the North Sea
OL,7,Fhave "much more to do" if the sector
OL,8,Fis to meet its targets for reducing
OL,9,Femissions in 2040 and 2050, a report
OL,10,Fhas found.
OL,12,FThe North Sea Transition Authority
OL,13,F(NSTA) said in its report that the
OL,14,Falready agreed target for the sector
OL,15,Fof halving emissions between 2018 and
OL,16,F2030 "is well within reach on the
OL,17,Fcurrent trajectory".
