OL,3,CNorth Sea has 'much more to do' to
OL,4,Cmeet emissions targets for 2040 onwards
OL,6,FBut it added that without further
OL,7,Finvestment "industry will not meet the
OL,8,F2040 target of reducing emissions by
OL,9,F90% or the 2050 net zero target".
OL,11,FThe NSTA made clear in its latest
OL,12,Femissions monitoring report that it
OL,13,F"expects the whole industry to rise to
OL,14,Fthe challenge on emissions reduction".
OL,16,FIt issued the warning as it detailed
OL,17,Fhow emissions from the oil and gas
OL,18,Fsector in the UK Continental Shelf
OL,19,F(UKCS) had fallen by an estimated 7%
OL,20,Fbetween 2023 and 2024.
