OL,6,FThis is the fifth year in a row
OL,7,Femissions have gone down, the report
OL,8,Fnoted, with this "contributing to a
OL,9,Ftotal decrease of 34% between 2018 and
OL,10,F2024.
OL,12,FThe report also noted that flaring `
OL,13,Fthe controlled burning of gas produced
OL,14,Fas part of the process of extracting
OL,15,Foil ` had fallen by 4.8% in 2024 to
OL,16,F658 million cubic metres ` with this
OL,17,Fbeing the lowest level on record, and
OL,18,F51% lower than in 2018.
