OL,4,Cmeet emissions targets for 2040 onwards
OL,6,FCommenting on the report, NSTA
OL,7,Fdirector of strategy Hedvig Ljungerud
OL,8,Fsaid: "Bringing down production
OL,9,Femissions by more than a third in six
OL,10,Fyears shows the North Sea oil and gas
OL,11,Findustry has been getting a lot right,
OL,12,Freflecting its commitment."
OL,14,FHowever, she added: "If operators lose
OL,15,Ffocus on the task at hand, the
OL,16,Fprojections are clear that UK
OL,17,Fproduction will become less clean and
OL,18,Fless competitive compared with imports
OL,19,Fover time."
