OL,3,CNorth Sea has 'much more to do' to
OL,4,Cmeet emissions targets for 2040 onwards
OL,6,FMs Ljungerud continued: "While the UK
OL,7,Fstill consumes oil and gas, the way it
OL,8,Fis produced must become progressively
OL,9,Fcleaner.
OL,11,F"We're encouraged that good work has
OL,12,Fbegun, but there is still much more to
OL,13,Fdo.
OL,15,F"It is time to commit to serious,
OL,16,Flarge-scale investments in emissions
OL,17,Freduction, and secure a leading role
OL,18,Fin the North Sea's transition into a
OL,19,Fclean energy powerhouse."
