OL,6,FThe report meanwhile stressed the need
OL,7,Ffor "seriousinvestments in emissions
OL,8,Freduction" if the 2040 and 2050
OL,9,Ftargets are to be met.
OL,11,FThe NSTA said: "It is only through
OL,12,Fbold action that the sector can retain
OL,13,Fits social licence to operate and play
OL,14,Fa key role in establishing a world-
OL,15,Fleading offshore clean energy industry
OL,16,Fin the UK.
OL,18,F"Recent progress clearly shows that
OL,19,Fmany operators are stepping up and
OL,20,Fsetting positive examples for their
OL,21,Fpeers to follow.
